        "titulo": "¡Retiro exitoso!",
        "html": "<table align=\"center\" border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" width=\"100%\" class=\"gla-mail-size-container\" style=\"border-collapse: collapse;mso-table-lspace: 0pt;mso-table-rspace: 0pt; max-width: 600px !important; margin: auto;\">\n    <tbody>\n       <tr>\n          <td>\n             <table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" width=\"100%\" style=\"min-width: 100%;border-collapse: collapse;mso-table-lspace: 0pt;mso-table-rspace: 0pt;\">\n                <tbody>\n                   <tr>\n                      <td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" style=\"padding-right: 0px;padding-left: 0px;padding-top: 0;padding-bottom: 0;text-align: center; margin: auto;\">\n                         <img src=\"https://componentesui.blob.core.windows.net/recursos/iconografia-gla/estados-de-envio/relleno/png/entregado-%20domicilio-verde.png\" style=\"margin: auto; display: inline-block !important; border: 0;width:80px;height: auto;outline: none;text-decoration: none;-ms-interpolation-mode: bicubic; mso-line-height-rule: at-least;\" alt=\"\" title=\"Icono\">\n                      </td>\n                   </tr>\n                   <tr>\n                      <td valign=\"top\" align=\"center \">\n                         <h1 class=\"gla-h4\" style=\"font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: #616161; font-size: 18px; font-weight: bold; line-height: 26px; text-align: center; margin: 0; padding: 0;\">¡Retiro exitoso!</h1>\n                         <p class=\"gla-h5\" style=\" font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: #757575; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; text-align: center; margin: 0; padding: 0; \"><em>Tracking general N° 3100000345678</em></p>\n                      </td>\n                   </tr>\n                </tbody>\n             </table>\n          </td>\n       </tr>\n       <tr>\n          <td valign=\"top \" style=\"padding: 0px; padding-top: 38px;\" class=\"gla-text-container text-line-height\">\n             <table width=\"100%\" cellspacing=\"0 \" cellpadding=\"0 \" border=\"0 \" style=\"min-width: 100%;border-collapse: collapse;mso-table-lspace: 0pt;mso-table-rspace: 0pt;\">\n                <tbody>\n                   <tr>\n                      <td valign=\"top \" align=\"left\" style=\"padding-bottom:15px;\">\n                         <h2 class=\"gla-h1\" style=\"font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: #d71920; font-size: 23px; font-weight: bold; line-height: 27px; margin: 0; padding: 0;\"> Hola Sofía García,</h2>\n                      </td>\n                   </tr>\n                   <tr>\n                      <td valign=\"top \" align=\"left\" style=\" font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: #616161; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0; padding: 0; padding-bottom: 15px; \">Ya realizamos la colecta de tus paquetes en tu domicilio.</td>\n                   </tr>\n                   <tr>\n                      <td valign=\"top \" align=\"left\" style=\" font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: #616161; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0; padding: 0; padding-bottom: 15px; \"><i>¡Gracias por contratar nuestro servicio!</i></td>\n                   </tr>\n                </tbody>\n             </table>\n          </td>\n       </tr>\n       <tr>\n          <td valign=\"top\" align=\"center\" style=\"padding-top:15px; padding-bottom: 40px; \">\n          </td>\n       </tr>\n       <tr>\n          <td class=\"text-line-height\" style=\"font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: #616161; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0; padding: 0; padding-bottom: 15px;\">\n             Te invitamos a <a style=\"color: #d71920; font-size: inherit; text-decoration: none;\" href=\"https://surveys.hotjar.com/6b1dfef8-addc-4ba9-afd0-5ea71d9eef3c\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color:#d71920; font-size: inherit;\">calificar la experiencia</span></a>. Tu opinión es muy importante para que podamos mejorar.\n          <br><br><br></td>\n       </tr>\n       <tr>\n          <td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" style=\"border-top: 0; border-bottom: 0; margin: 0;padding: 0;\">\n             <table align=\"center \" border=\"0 \" cellpadding=\"0 \" cellspacing=\"0 \" width=\"100% \" class=\"gla-mail-size-container\" style=\"border-collapse: collapse;mso-table-lspace: 0pt;mso-table-rspace: 0pt;max-width: 700px !important; margin: auto; \">\n                <tbody bgcolor=\"#eeeeee\">\n                   <tr>\n                      <td valign=\"top\" class=\"gla-text-container gla-td-title-container\" style=\"padding-left: 18px;word-break: break-word;\">\n                         <h2 class=\"gla-h2\" style=\"font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;color: #d71920;font-size: 18px;font-weight: bold;line-height:27px;margin: 0;margin-top: 1rem;padding: 0;\">Te dejamos algunos tips...</h2>\n                      </td>\n                   </tr>\n                   <tr>\n                      <td valign=\"top\" class=\"gla-text-container text-line-height\" style=\"padding: 8px 18px 18px; word-break: break-word; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 26px;\"><ul><li><font color=\"#757575\"><b>Compartí con tu cliente el número de envío que figura en la etiqueta</b>, para que pueda realizar el seguimiento en </font><a href=\"https://www.andreani.com/\" style=\"\"><font color=\"#ce0000\">Andreani.com</font></a><font color=\"#757575\">. Recordá que vos también podrás hacerlo, desde el historial envíos en tu cuenta PyME.</font></li><li><font color=\"#757575\">Una vez que se haya concretado la entrega, <b>comunicate con el destinatario </b>para conocer cómo fue su experiencia.</font></li></ul></td>\n                   </tr>\n                </tbody>\n             </table><br><br><br>\n          </td>\n       </tr>\n   </tbody>\n</table>",
